            <Col id="title04">Previous item</Col>
            <Col id="title05_1">Make sure to &lt;fc v='#ff6969'&gt;report&lt;/fc&gt; school violence!</Col>
            <Col id="title05_2">There will be absolutely &lt;b v='true'&gt;&lt;fc v='#fef0d2'&gt;no repercussions&lt;/fc&gt;&lt;/b&gt; due to the content of your answers, and we will keep them confidential.</Col>
