            <Col id="title05_3">report</Col>
            <Col id="title13">* Responses to these questions will be provided to the school and the police, and they are intended to assist the students who are experiencing difficulty due to school violence. Your honest responses will be a big assistance in resolving the cases. Would you like to answer?</Col>
