            <Col id="alertTitle17">Would you like to save the draft?</Col>
            <Col id="alertTitle12_2">You may log onto the Student Survey on School Violence website at any time during the survey period to submit the report. (You will need a personal authentication number)</Col>
            <Col id="alertTitle13_2">Be sure to watch the following material concerning the guidelines on school violence prevention and report.</Col>
            <Col id="ins01">① Who (Perpetrator: name of the student who harassed “other friend (student)” or “me”)</Col>
